{"tid":997130,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇公務員/紀律部隊巴絲打好熟啲房屋福利？","createTime":"2019-01-27T01:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T05:01:07.000Z","uid":19350,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b77cca554ab095632f1add4b56040457883b5ae","tid":997130,"uid":19350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:39:32.000Z","msg":"我係就快夠3年既紀律部隊人員<br />\n我未婚 排單人公屋實冇我份<br />\n所以想問下係咪申請就會有綠表資格？<br />\n定係申請完都係要抽綠表資格？<br />\n同埋我係公屋住戶 戶主係我老豆<br />\n如果我好彩抽到綠表買到居屋係咪只係除名就冇問題？<br />\n定係我要除左名先可以去抽綠表買居屋？<br />\n另外如果個一年抽中左 但我12個月內冇買到居屋<br />\n綠表失左效 咁樣會唔會影響到我之後申請綠表？<br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c6ed9b937a433057196eadf78b6bb382684528","tid":997130,"uid":151071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b263b5435296c54af2ec2bb0d2c4a2be16b6047","tid":997130,"uid":19350,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f5c6ed9b937a433057196eadf78b6bb382684528","tid":997130,"uid":151071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"以我認知應該係可以直接申請綠表架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果要上到公屋先可以申請綠表 咁我單身咪姐係冇乜可能"},{"pid":"378c8d23a3c84e46ff7c7d7da328f412c6742494","tid":99713